      <bioghist id="ref2">
         <head>Biographical Sketch</head>
         <p>Hatcher was made Curator of Paleontology and Osteology at the Carnegie Museum in Pittsburgh.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="ref4">
         <head>Description of the Material</head>
         <p>The archives of John Bell Hatcher are from his time collecting at Yale (1884-1892) include notebooks (personal and field), correspondence and some biographical materials.</p>  
